sentences.english: Changes in proteins of Semimembranosus and Biceps muscles mainly happened during curing and fermentation.

sentences.english: For biceps I recommend doing dumbbell preacher curls.
sentences.chinese: 對肱二頭肌，我推薦啞鈴彎舉。

sentences.english: The French midfielder, replaced in the 39th minute, has strained the biceps femoris muscle in his right leg.
sentences.chinese: 達科特則因爲拉傷了右腿二頭肌而在39分鐘被換下。

sentences.english: “The bicep alone—and this is a conservative estimate—could curl 430 pounds,” Conrad says.
sentences.chinese: 保守估計，霸王龍的二頭肌有430磅的曲力。

sentences.english: Measure around the fullest part of the biceps, fairly generously.
sentences.chinese: 十分寬鬆地圍量二頭肌最豐滿處。

sentences.english: My left bicep is smaller than my right one.
sentences.chinese: 我左邊的二頭肌小於我的權利之一。

sentences.english: Closed traumatic disruption of the biceps brachii is an infrequent injury.
sentences.chinese: 外傷造成肱二頭肌封閉性的斷裂是一罕見的傷害。

sentences.english: When bending the elbow the biceps are the agonist.
sentences.chinese: 曲肘時，肱二頭肌會收縮。

sentences.english: Conclusions There was a tendon plate in Biceps brachii of rabbit, muscle fibers arranged into ring-pennate shape.
sentences.chinese: 結論家兔肱二頭肌內有一腱板，肌束排列成環羽狀。

sentences.english: Extend your left arm, flex the bicep and hold.
sentences.chinese: 伸展你的左臂，收縮你的二頭肌，保持這個姿勢。

sentences.english: A personal trainer. Thank heaven. Can you take a look at my right bicep? I seemed to have strained it.
sentences.chinese: 私人教練。感謝上帝。你能看看我右手的二頭肌麼？

sentences.english: You can’t flex your biceps all the time.
sentences.chinese: 你不能不停地伸縮你的二頭肌，對吧？
